Goal
* Please add at the beginning that the clash occurs in Reverse mode only.

Cases
* Please ensure that each test and its corresponding validator are similar, especially when only Reverse mode is enabled. Specifically,

  • Revise the cases to ensure that the outputs in each pair are of similar length.
  
  • Additionally, the outputs should either both exceed 2 ** 32 or neither should exceed in each pair.
  
  • Test 3: Add leading zeros to the beginning of the input.

* Some digits aren't covered in the visible tests. Please add/modify tests to include such digits: 4, 6, 7, 8.

* The digit 8 isn't covered in the validators. Please add/modify validators to include this digit.

Thanks.

✅ Approved the contribution.
Comment: Good puzzle
